## 7. UI / Theme system (greyscale, premium, Archon-discipline + Capricorn-cinema)

A **monochrome system** — shades of grey, white, black — with a single restrained "signal" accent (a cold, desaturated near-platinum) used sparingly, plus locked semantic state colors.

- **Tokens (dark "Graphite" default):** canvas `#0A0A0B` · surface-1 `#111113` · surface-2 `#17181B` · surface-3 `#1F2024` · code/terminal `#070708` · border-subtle `rgba(255,255,255,0.06)` · border-emphasis `#2A2C31`. Text: hi `#F4F5F6`, mid `#A7ABB2`, low `#6A6E76`. **Signal accent:** a single cold near-white/platinum `#E8EAED` for active/CTA, with `#9DA7B3` cool-steel for links/active-nav. (Optionally one whisper of cyan-grey for "live" dots only.)
- **Semantic (locked, global):** success/settled `#4ADE80`-muted → use desaturated; pending `#F5B544`; failed `#FF6B6B`; info `#7FA8C9`. Render as pill: color at ~14% bg, full-opacity text, 1px border ~30%.
- **Type:** heavy geometric grotesk (General Sans / Clash) for display; **Inter** for UI; **JetBrains Mono / Geist Mono** for amounts, hashes, rates, chain IDs (perfect for nanopayment figures like `$0.000001`). Eyebrows: small uppercase mono, +0.12em, in low-grey. Self-hosted fonts, no CDN, no layout shift.
- **Motif:** thin luminous **horizon line** (Capricorn) + flowing **metered particles** through a gate (the "sluice"). Survives elsewhere as 1px line-art only.
- **3D hero:** prefer a **performant** approach — react-three-fiber single particle-stream, or a 2.5D layered SVG/canvas meter. (Archon ruled heavy three.js a bundle/time trap; Capricorn got cinematic with a light particle field. Stay light; one orchestrated load animation; respect `prefers-reduced-motion` with a static state.)
- **Shell:** 264px left sidebar (surface-1) + 64px top utility bar (workspace switcher, global ⌘K search, Arc network "Live" badge + dot, wallet chip). 12px card radius, hairline borders, soft shadows. Identical brand/badges/type across every page — "one platform, not ten mockups."
- **Reusable primitives:** Logo, NetworkBadge (Arc live dot), MeterCard (live accrual + sparkline), AmountMono (tabular `$0.000001`), ReceiptCard (units/rate/batch tx/verified), BondCard (staked/slashed), AgentTrace (reasoning steps), Stepper, AddressChip (mono+copy), DataRow, Tabs, Tooltip, Skeleton, Toast, Modal, ThemeToggle. Dev-only `/app/_dev/tokens` page renders every primitive in every state (sign-off surface before features).

