- **Frontend:** Next.js 15 (App Router, TS strict) · Tailwind · shadcn/ui (restyled) · lucide-react · Recharts (analytics) · Framer Motion · react-three-fiber *or* light SVG/canvas (hero) · **viem/wagmi + Reown AppKit** (wallet: email/social/wallet) · self-hosted fonts.
