- **Backend:** NestJS or Fastify (TS). Postgres (or SQLite for speed) for meter ledger, receipts, registry, agents. Redis optional (rate-limit / batch timers) — **no Docker required**; run on your VPS directly with pm2/systemd.
- **Payments:** `@x402/*` SDKs + **Circle CLI** (`@circle-fin/cli`) + Gateway Nanopayments client. **ARC CLI** (Canteen-hosted testnet RPC + Arc context for the coding agent).
- **Contracts:** Hardhat/Foundry · ERC-8004 (Identity/Reputation/Validation) — use a minimal reference impl · RoyaltySplitter · Bond/Escrow. Deploy to Arc testnet; verify on Arcscan.
- **Agent:** lightweight runtime; **OpenAI gpt-4o-mini** (your $5 credit, capped) or Claude Haiku via API; Circle Skills + MCP for tool wiring.
- **Hosting:** Frontend on Netlify/Vercel; API + agent on your 200GB VPS (pm2). Docs on the same Next app or a Fumadocs subroute.

